SourceURI: https://github.com/ChimeraTK/ControlSystemAdapter-EPICS-IOC-Adapter
Maintainer: Martin Hierholzer <martin.hierholzer@desy.de>
Section: libs
License: lgpl3
Target-repositories: intern pub

Has-packages: dev-noheader lib

Dependencies: doxygen libchimeratk-controlsystemadapter-dev libreadline-dev
Dependencies-dev: libchimeratk-controlsystemadapter-dev

Description-dev: Header and cmake files for the EPICS R3.16 IOC Adapter for the ChimeraTK ControlSystemAdapter. The files you need to compile against libchimeratk-controlsystemadaper-epics-ioc-adapter.
Description-lib: libchimeratk-controlsystemadapter-epics-ioc-adapter provides the EPICS R3.16 IOC adapter for the ChimeraTK ControlSystemAdapter. Linking against this library will make an EPICS R3.16 IOC out of any control application built against the ChimeraTK ControlSystemAdapter.

Override-auto-configure-flags: -DEPICS_VERSION="3"

Install-additional-pattern-dev: usr/share/ChimeraTK-ControlSystemAdapter-EPICS-IOC-Adapter/*
